channel.description:
This is my first release by the way.
This is only about 35 percent done. Server is not finished Quit it because People are idiots. (Like me sometimes) But i'm not that much of an idiot that often.

Custom Shop 1 There is whip, Tuna Potato doesnt not work, was in progress of making it. [img]http://i26.tinypic.com/2helwdj.jpg[/img]
Custom Shop 2 [img]http://i27.tinypic.com/29uy2di.jpg[/img] Whip in it..
Mining from delta [img]http://i30.tinypic.com/11j98bc.jpg[/img]
Smithing, i added mith + [img]http://i29.tinypic.com/11cdti1.jpg[/img]
